text: Jack W. Williams is an American politician. He is a member of the Alabama Senate representing the 34th District, since 2018. He was a member of the Alabama House of Representatives from the 102nd District, serving since 2014. He is a member of the Republican party. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Members of the Alabama House of Representatives Category:Alabama Republicans Category:21st-century American politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Alabama state senators
